{"type": "article", "id": 7786, "title": "Andy Warhol 积木熊", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-26T07:32:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052346384av9SBMtcGFeVJnf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tAndy Warhol 的粉丝最近可以关注一下 日本玩具生产商 Medicom Toy 的最新作品，为了致敬这位波普艺术大师，Medicom Toy 推出了一款崭新的 Bearbricks 积木熊。这款经典小熊全身披满靓丽的波普配色，有着 Andy Warhol 标志性的墨镜和高颧骨。目前定价为 75 美元，<a href=\"http://www.bearbrick.com/bea_aw/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052346376R258mVQfWxbkJzj.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234637j2iuVxePXhnaQO3z.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}